article_title: Rubio says American dream must be preserved
article_text:
North Andover, MA (01845)

Today

Sunny along with a few clouds. High around 85F. Winds WNW at 5 to 10 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy early with increasing clouds overnight. Slight chance of a rain shower. Low near 60F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph.

article_metadata.author: Doug Ireland direland@eagletribune.com

og.description: LONDONDERRY — For Florida Sen. Marco Rubio, it’s all about preserving the American dream.
